@node INFOS_GENERAL "Color-Riddle/Information/General"
I started the project "Color-Riddle" some years ago on my old Amiga 500 in AmigaBasic :-) But ich lost the interest for this very quick.
But when I downloaded AmigaE some months ago, I decided to program "Color-Riddle" first, because it isn't too large. But I hadn't much time and therefore it taked me a very long time to complete the program.

Please send me your suggestions and bug-reports. I also always search for translations (.catalog- and .guide-Files) in other languages (and a good english translation, of course).

I demand no fee or reward, but I would be pleased about every gift (i.e. little program written by you ;-)
@endnode


